			<action-date date="20130507">May 7, 2013</action-date>
			<action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="S000583">Mr. Smith of Texas</sponsor>
			 (for himself, <cosponsor name-id="S001176">Mr. Scalise</cosponsor>,
			 <cosponsor name-id="C001075">Mr. Cassidy</cosponsor>, and
			 <cosponsor name-id="W000215">Mr. Waxman</cosponsor>) introduced the following
